(left) Sensor placement on a cow; (right) PCB layout for the wearable device.

A firmware was developed to handle sensor data acquisition, feature extraction, and wireless communication. Accelerometers and gyroscopes from the IMUs were used to capture 16-bit mechanical vibration data, while methane concentration levels were collected from the Figaro\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
